	<Title>
		Stop nibbling your nails
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Biting your nails and picking at the cuticles can damage your nail beds, that part of your nails where the U-shaped cuticles begin. And even a minor cut alongside your nail can be an entry point for bacteria or fungi, leading to infection. So find a way to end this bad habit, starting today.&lt;/p&gt;
